This repository is missing the binary file:

  gradle-wrapper.jar

Without it, `./gradlew` cannot run and you will see:

  Could not find or load main class org.gradle.wrapper.GradleWrapperMain

Fix:
- Commit `android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar` generated by `gradle wrapper`, OR
- Install system gradle in CI and run gradle without wrapper (see CI_GRADLE_QUICKFIX.md).
